        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What HIPAA-compliant alternatives work with AI website builders?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Several HIPAA-compliant solutions integrate with AI website builders. JotForm Healthcare offers HIPAA-compliant forms that embed on any website - collects patient information, medical history, and intake forms securely. FormDr specializes in healthcare forms with HIPAA compliance, embeds easily, and offers BAA coverage. PatientSimple provides complete patient intake and scheduling with HIPAA compliance. These tools embed seamlessly on Squarespace, Wix, Framer, or Webflow sites. Workflow: website provides information and booking, then embed secure HIPAA-compliant forms for patient intake, or link to external HIPAA-compliant patient portal. Many healthcare providers use this hybrid approach successfully - AI builder for marketing and information, specialized healthcare forms for data collection. Always verify BAA coverage and consult legal counsel."
        }
      },
